column5: Looking for a site that has fishing reports for northwesternOntaio. Also lodge listings.Ben
Hey Ben,Check out http://www.justfishontario.comThe site has almost all the lodge listings for northwestern Ontario, plus fishing reports from some of the top lakes and lots of other good stuff.

Good map and lots of lodge listings at <http://www.heartland.on.ca> Patricia map is free by requesting online or you can phone 800 # there. Also www.ontariossunsetcountry.ca has a free map and directory of lodges. I own a lodge in NW Ontario, South Bay Lodge <www.southbaylodge.com> 42 miles NE of Ear Falls, boat-in on Confederation Lake, 14,000 acres. good luck roger
